ygData.messageBody:
will be very hard to get the pieces at lvl 11. especially since lower guk is
less crowded these days, and mistmoore is empty 7/24. so the mobs you need
the drops off are not killed too often for xp, and therefore there is only
small chance to get the drops.
only chance is get highlevel friends to help you kill the mobs for you.
